<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 06:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国监管机构出台更多卖空限制措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周二表示，将暂停券商借入股票进行借贷，并限制所谓的证券再融资规模，作为进一步遏制卖空行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟旨在就实现绿色工业雄心的关键路径达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/eu-aims-agree-key-path-towards-green-industry-ambitions-2024-02-06/</link><description>欧盟政策制定者希望周二达成新规则，促进太阳能、风能、燃料电池和其他清洁技术设备的国内生产，以确保其行业能够与中国和美国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/eu-aims-agree-key-path-towards-green-industry-ambitions-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>梅西希望在香港队表现不佳后参加东京友谊赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/messi-hopes-play-tokyo-friendly-after-hong-kong-letdown-2024-02-06/</link><description>周末缺席比赛，令众多香港球迷失望后，梅西保留了参加国际迈阿密在东京的友谊赛的可能性，并表示他离开时比几天前“好多了” 。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/messi-hopes-play-tokyo-friendly-after-hong-kong-letdown-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示反对并打击一切形式的网络攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆表示，中国政府不会容忍任何形式的网络攻击，也不会允许任何国家和个人利用中国基础设施从事此类非法活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国反弹亚洲股市上涨，美元稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</link><description>由于遭受重创的中国市场反弹，亚洲股市周二小幅上涨，但其他地区的投资者因美联储近期降息的预期减弱而持谨慎态度，这反过来又支撑了美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:35:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：外交部长称台湾盟友危地马拉正在考虑与中国建立商业关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</link><description>中美洲国家危地马拉外交部长周一告诉路透社，危地马拉正在考虑与中国建立正式贸易关系，但计划维持与台湾的现有关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>雪、冰阻碍了数百万中国人春节前的回家之旅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</link><description>冻雨、雪和冰使中国中部和东部地区的许多人的回家之路变得复杂，数十亿人在春节前在寒冷的天气中出行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>日本SMBC聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁斯托尔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</link><description>日本三井住友银行（SMBC）周二表示，已聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁卡斯滕·斯托尔（Carsten Stoehr）担任亚太区副行长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:15:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>美元稳定，澳元因加息前景而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</link><description>由于美联储今年不太可能大幅降息的预期不断升温，美元周二稳定在三个月高位附近，而澳元在央行表示不排除再次加息后上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>泰国相信援助努力将引发缅甸危机对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</link><description>泰国一名高级官员表示，泰国领导的一项新的人道主义倡议旨在为军事统治的缅甸交战阵营之间的谈判铺平道路，三年前，一场政变引发了全国各地的不稳定和暴力浪潮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国法院对澳大利亚作家缓刑的判决“令人愤慨”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周二表示，北京一家法院以间谍罪名判处澳大利亚作家杨恒均死刑缓期执行，这是一种“愤慨”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部团队前往中国讨论补贴和经济政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</link><description>一位财政部官员周一表示，拜登政府本周已派出五名美国财政部高级官员前往北京进行经济会谈，其中将包括中国增加过剩工业产能的“非市场”政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：澳洲联储关注美国债券收益率飙升蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>Stake F1车队以双重身份规避赌博限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</link><description>索伯运营的 Stake 一级方程式车队本赛季将以两个名字参加比赛，以遵守一些国家的赌博限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 20:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院共和党人考虑边境协议，众议院同行敦促拒绝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</link><description>美国参议院两党加强边境安全法案的首席共和党谈判代表表示，他的核心小组应在周二之前决定是否就该提案展开辩论，而众议院共和党领导人则敦促废除该协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>